{"article_id":"z0TBDSVYP4nQKsY7","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Story highlights","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Attorney General Holder :","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"Prosecutors to `` doggedly follow the facts ''","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"McCain charges","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"Obama did n't `` unequivocally '' say","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"that no leaks came from White House","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"Congressional leaders seek to halt increasing leaks of classified information","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"Attorney General Eric Holder said on Friday","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"he had assigned two U.S. attorneys","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"to lead investigations into the possible leaking of state secrets .","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"`` The unauthorized disclosure of classified information can compromise the security of this country and all Americans ,","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"and it will not be tolerated , ''","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"he said in a statement .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"Holder assigned U.S. Attorney for the District of Columbia Ronald C. Machen Jr. , a Democratic appointee , and U.S. Attorney for the District of Maryland Rod J. Rosenstein , a holdover GOP appointee ,","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"to lead the investigations .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"`` These two highly respected and experienced prosecutors will be directing separate investigations","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"currently being conducted by the FBI .","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"I have every confidence in their abilities","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"to doggedly follow the facts and the evidence in the pursuit of justice","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"wherever it leads , ''","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"said Holder .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"JUST WATCHED McCain :","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"Leaks came from the White House","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"MUST WATCH McCain :","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"Leaks came from the White House","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"01:00","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"JUST WATCHED Ruppersberger :","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"Leaks worst he 's seen","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"MUST WATCH Ruppersberger :","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"Leaks worst he 's seen","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"02:36","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"Leaks probe not 'finger-pointing '","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"Leaks probe not 'finger-pointing ' 01:31","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"Earlier Friday , President Barack Obama strongly rejected claims","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"that his White House has deliberately leaked secrets to the media ,","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"the idea was `` offensive ''","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"and would put Americans at risk .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"Some Republicans ,","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"led by veteran Sen. John McCain of Arizona ,","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"alleged","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"that the White House must be knowingly involved","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"because of the nature of the leaked information .","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"But Obama pushed back angrily","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"as he was questioned on the issue at a news conference ,","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"that he had `` zero tolerance '' for such leaks","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"and that those responsible would `` suffer consequences . '' `` The notion","depth":16},{"id":53,"text":"that the White House would purposely release classified national security information","depth":16},{"id":54,"text":"is offensive ,","depth":15},{"id":55,"text":"it 's wrong ,","depth":14},{"id":56,"text":"and people ,","depth":15},{"id":57,"text":"I think ,","depth":15},{"id":58,"text":"need to have a better sense of how I approach this office and how the people around me approach this office , ''","depth":14},{"id":59,"text":"he said .","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"`` We are dealing with issues","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"that can touch on the safety and security of the American people","depth":14},{"id":62,"text":"-- our families or our military or our allies --","depth":14},{"id":63,"text":"and so we do n't play with that . ''","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"Intelligence leaks are a source of consistent frustration for his administration","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"as they have been for others ,","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"he said ,","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"and the White House will carry out `` thorough investigations . ''","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"In response , McCain said","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"Obama was distancing himself from the controversy .","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"`` What the president did not unequivocally say today is that none of the classified or highly sensitive information","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"recently leaked to the media","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"came from the White House , ''","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"McCain said .","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"`` I continue to call on the president to immediately appoint a special counsel","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"to fully investigate","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"and ,","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"where necessary ,","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"prosecute these gravely serious breaches of our national security . ''","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"A report in The New York Times last week","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"that provided classified details of what it described as a U.S cyberattack","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"targeting Iran 's nuclear centrifuge program","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"sparked the bipartisan outrage .","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"Obama also repeated the statements","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"made by the writers of the articles in question","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"that the White House was not the source of their information .","depth":6},{"id":86,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":6},{"id":87,"text":"Obama :","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"Eurozone success is 'good for us '","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":5},{"id":90,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"Obama :","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"Eurozone success is 'good for us '","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"01:54","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"Getting tough on intelligence leaks","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"Getting tough on intelligence leaks","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"01:51","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"White House leaks spark controversy","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"White House leaks spark controversy","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"02:07","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"Other recent possible leaks of classified information included details on the administration 's efforts","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"to expand its drone program","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"and Obama 's involvement in `` kill lists '' against militants in Yemen and Pakistan .","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"The public airing of details","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"surrounding a recently disrupted bomb plot in Yemen by al Qaeda in the Arabian Peninsula","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"also angered intelligence and national security officials .","depth":7},{"id":112,"text":"Congressional leaders said earlier Friday","depth":6},{"id":113,"text":"that those responsible","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"for endangering national security","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"by leaking classified information to the media","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"should be sent to jail .","depth":7},{"id":117,"text":"Republican Rep. Mike Rogers of Michigan , the House Intelligence Committee chairman , said","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"that it was not yet known who was behind the leaks","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"but that someone `` committed a crime","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"that is having serious consequences to our national security . ''","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"Bipartisan efforts are needed","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"to identify whoever is responsible for the leaks ,","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"involving a cyberwarfare program against Iran and other intelligence matters ,","depth":13},{"id":124,"text":"and `` make sure","depth":14},{"id":125,"text":"that leaker goes to jail , ''","depth":14},{"id":126,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"Rep. Dutch Ruppersberger of Maryland , the top Democrat on the House panel , echoed Rogers ' call","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"for the leaker to be `` held accountable . ''","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"Speaking in the House on Friday ,","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"Republican Rep. Mo Brooks of Alabama asked ,","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"`` where is the outrage from the White House about these leaks ? ''","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"He called for the White House `` to get off the campaign trail ,","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"show leadership ,","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"do the president 's job","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"and aggressively pursue the leakers of America 's state secrets . ''","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"Leaks not only compromise national security efforts ,","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"they discourage allies from trusting in the United States ,","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"Brooks said .","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"`` It 's time for the president to plug the holes","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"and protect America 's national security , ''","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"Rogers said Friday","depth":8},{"id":143,"text":"that the recent leaks are `` a hundred times the magnitude '' of those in the Valerie Plame case","depth":9},{"id":144,"text":"and that `` someone needs to pay a price for this crime . ''","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"Former Vice President Dick Cheney 's chief of staff , Lewis `` Scooter '' Libby , was convicted in 2007 in connection with the leaking of CIA officer Plame 's identity","depth":8},{"id":146,"text":"-- information","depth":10},{"id":147,"text":"that was technically classified ,","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"though Cheney later implied","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"that information had been declassified .","depth":10},{"id":150,"text":"Ruppersberger said","depth":8},{"id":151,"text":"it was vital that bipartisan efforts were made","depth":9},{"id":152,"text":"to `` follow the facts","depth":10},{"id":153,"text":"wherever they go ''","depth":10},{"id":154,"text":"but reiterated","depth":8},{"id":155,"text":"that the source of the information was not known .","depth":8},{"id":156,"text":"`` These leaks have been occurring more and more , ''","depth":9},{"id":157,"text":"he said ,","depth":9},{"id":158,"text":"adding","depth":9},{"id":159,"text":"that they were the worst","depth":10},{"id":160,"text":"he had seen in nearly 10 years on the intelligence panel .","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"The leaks could come from within Congress or the executive branch ,","depth":8},{"id":162,"text":"he acknowledged .","depth":8},{"id":163,"text":"The Intelligence Committee leaders met Thursday with FBI Director Robert Mueller ,","depth":10},{"id":164,"text":"whose agency is investigating the leaks ,","depth":10},{"id":165,"text":"according to legislators .","depth":9},{"id":166,"text":"Specifically , the FBI has launched an investigation into apparent leaks of classified information","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"involving the cyberwarfare program against Iran ,","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"a U.S. official said this week .","depth":10},{"id":169,"text":"The agency is also investigating the thwarted Yemen plot ,","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"according to Mueller .","depth":11},{"id":171,"text":"In its report , The New York Times said","depth":12},{"id":172,"text":"that since shortly after he became president ,","depth":13},{"id":173,"text":"Obama has ordered cyberattacks","depth":14},{"id":174,"text":"targeting computers","depth":15},{"id":175,"text":"that run Iran 's nuclear enrichment facilities .","depth":15},{"id":176,"text":"It attributed the information to participants in the program .","depth":11},{"id":177,"text":"McCain , the ranking Republican on the Senate Armed Services Committee , alleged","depth":10},{"id":178,"text":"that the White House authorized the leaks for political gain .","depth":10},{"id":179,"text":"`` These leaks clearly were not done in the interest of national security","depth":11},{"id":180,"text":"or to reveal corrupt or illegal actions","depth":12},{"id":181,"text":"about which the public has a right","depth":14},{"id":182,"text":"to know ,","depth":14},{"id":183,"text":"as in the case of legitimate whistleblowers , ''","depth":13},{"id":184,"text":"McCain said .","depth":10},{"id":185,"text":"`` It is difficult to escape the conclusion","depth":9},{"id":186,"text":"that these recent leaks of highly classified information ,","depth":11},{"id":187,"text":"all","depth":12},{"id":188,"text":"of which have the effect","depth":13},{"id":189,"text":"of making the president look strong and decisive on national security in the middle of his re-election campaign ,","depth":13},{"id":190,"text":"have a deeper political motivation . ''","depth":10},{"id":191,"text":"The White House pushed back ,","depth":7},{"id":192,"text":"with spokesman Jay Carney saying","depth":8},{"id":193,"text":"that `` this administration takes all appropriate and necessary steps","depth":9},{"id":194,"text":"to prevent leaks of classified information or sensitive information","depth":10},{"id":195,"text":"that could risk ongoing counterterrorism or intelligence o